text: haey chea karpit nasa yeung ban bratan kompir( ta vr t ning ainh chi l) ning kramochbab haeyning pheap chea na pi dl ambaur ai sra- el haey yeung ban bratan leaphosakkar da la cheachraen dl puokke promteang yeung ban leukatamkeung puokke aoy khpangkhpasa( cheang brachacheate neanea) leu piphoplok( neasamynoh)
